---
import PolicyLayout from '../../layouts/PolicyLayout.astro';
---

<PolicyLayout
	title="Cookie Policy"
	description="Cookie Policy for the Audius Song of the Day Discord bot."
>
	<h2>Overview</h2>
	<p>
		Audius Song of the Day does not intentionally use cookies for tracking,
		advertising, profiling, or analytics purposes.
	</p>

	<h2>Essential Website Functionality</h2>
	<p>
		The website may rely on standard browser and hosting functionality
		necessary for delivering pages and maintaining security. Such
		functionality may involve temporary technical data handled by your
		browser or hosting infrastructure.
	</p>

	<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
	<p>
		Links to external websites, including Discord, Audius, GitHub, and other
		third-party services, are governed by the cookie and privacy practices
		of those providers.
	</p>

	<h2>Future Changes</h2>
	<p>
		If analytics, advertising, or additional cookie-based technologies are
		introduced in the future, this Cookie Policy will be updated
		accordingly.
	</p>

	<h2>Contact</h2>
	<p>
		Questions regarding this Cookie Policy may be directed to{' '}
		<a href="mailto:toby@tobezdev.com">toby@tobezdev.com</a>.
	</p>
</PolicyLayout>
